data.description: Beautiful, executive townhome nestled in a gated community on a quiet street in the heart of the Biltmore corridor. High ceilings, light flooding in from the story high windows, open kitchen with breakfast nook. Two extended bedroom suites with space for your office, all bedrooms have walk in closets and huge windows. Attached garage, quiet community with pool, community center, on-sight management and a few blocks to extensive shopping, restaurants and the 51 freeway. Quiet city living at its best!
